OL,3,CCommunity arts project recognises work
OL,4,Cof activist
OL,6,FAn arts charity in Liverpool is
OL,7,Fcelebrating the work of community
OL,8,Factivist Dorothy Kuya.
OL,10,FDorothy, who died ten years ago, was
OL,11,Fwell known in the city and beyond for
OL,12,Fher work fighting racism and
OL,13,Fcampaigning for regeneration in
OL,14,Fdeprived areas.
OL,16,FNow the arts organisation is working
OL,17,Fwith Dorothy's family to showcase her
OL,18,Factivism and the impact and legacy of
OL,19,Fit.
