OL,6,FTammi Agatha, who joined Dorothy's
OL,7,Ffamily through her partner Paul, said:
OL,8,F"She embraced everybody, and wanted to
OL,9,Fhelp everybody.
OL,11,F"Even to this day, we bump into people
OL,12,Fand they say 'Oh Auntie Dot, she
OL,13,Fhelped me years ago'."
OL,15,FBorn in Granby in 1933, Dorothy began
OL,16,Fher activism as a teenager.
