OL,6,FShe later became Liverpool's first
OL,7,Fcommunity relations officer, and led
OL,8,Fthe successful campaign to establish
OL,9,Fthe city's International Slavery
OL,10,FMuseum.
OL,12,F"The biggest thing I picked up from
OL,13,Fher was community, and she was a
OL,14,Fstrong campaigner and activist over
OL,15,Fall those years, but she was
OL,16,Ffundamentally about community," Tammi
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,19,FPaul Ogolo, Dorothy's nephew, added
OL,20,Fthat she had a real impact on his life.
