OL,6,FDorothy was also a key member of the
OL,7,FGranby Residents Association (GRA)
OL,8,Fthat was established to save the
OL,9,Fneighbourhood.
OL,11,F"The Granby area which was Dorothy's
OL,12,Flocal area, she was active in the
OL,13,Fearly formation of GRA when the area
OL,14,Ffaced compulsory purchase and
OL,15,Fdemolition by Liverpool City Council,"
OL,16,Fsaid Ms Heneghan.
