OL,6,FOver the course of her life, Dorothy
OL,7,Fsaved letters, photos and information
OL,8,Fthat showed all the work she did and
OL,9,Fher family decided they wanted to
OL,10,Fshare it with the community. Her
OL,11,Farchives are now accessible at the
OL,12,FMaritime Museums Archive Centre.
OL,14,F"We realised, as soon as Auntie Dot
OL,15,Fpassed, the volume of books and we're
OL,16,Ftalking thousands - they just couldn't
OL,17,Fbe left, they had to be shared with
OL,18,Fother people," said Ms Agatha.
