OL,3,CCommunity arts project recognises work
OL,4,Cof activist
OL,6,F"Auntie Dot was all about education.
OL,7,FWhen we had this huge collection, the
OL,8,Fhouse wasn't big enough to house it so
OL,9,Fwe decided to approach the museum."
OL,11,FMs Heneghan continued: "There's an
OL,12,Fincredible amount of important
OL,13,Fdocumentation, photographs that span a
OL,14,Fhuge period.
OL,16,F"At the centre of this is really
OL,17,Fbringing in the community and to bring
OL,18,Ftheir own heritage to public access."
OL,20,FDorothy died in 2013, at the age of 80.
