OL,6,FFollowing her death she was recognised
OL,7,Fby Liverpool City Council, with a
OL,8,Fposthumous Citizen of Honour awards.
OL,10,F"It really means a lot...we are
OL,11,Fgrateful, we'd never forget her, and
OL,12,Fmost of the local people would never
OL,13,Fforget her," added Mr Ogolo.
OL,15,F"I'm grateful for everything everyone
OL,16,Fdoes to keep Auntie Dot's name alive."
